OL,3,CScottish Borders farmer shares fears
OL,4,Cfor industry due to rising costs
OL,6,FA Scottish Borders farmer has shared
OL,7,Fhis fears for the industry as conflict
OL,8,Fin the Middle East escalates.
OL,10,FJames Playfair-Hannay has warned that
OL,11,Fthere could be "gaps on the
OL,12,Fsupermarket shelves" as farmers see
OL,13,Ftheir costs go up.
OL,15,FInflation fears are growing as oil
OL,16,Fprices have soared to a four-year high.
OL,18,FSpeaking to ITV Border, James Playfair-
OL,19,FHannay said: "We just seem to be
OL,20,Fgetting an awful lot of challenges and
OL,21,Four costs of production keep going up.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/3
