OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1773061884
OL,3,CScottish Borders farmer shares fears
OL,4,Cfor industry due to rising costs
OL,6,F"National Insurance went up, the
OL,7,Fminimum wage is going up and fuel
OL,8,Fprices are now going up.
OL,10,F"One of these days many farmers are
OL,11,Fgoing to say enough is enough and
OL,12,Fthere will be gaps on the supermarket
OL,13,Fshelves."
OL,15,FFuel is one of the biggest costs to
OL,16,Ffarmers but they are also seeing an
OL,17,Fincrease in another key agricultural
OL,18,Fnecessity.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/3
