OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1773061884
OL,3,CScottish Borders farmer shares fears
OL,4,Cfor industry due to rising costs
OL,6,FJames Playfair-Hannay said: "The
OL,7,Ffertiliser prices appear to have gone
OL,8,Fup between #40 and #50 a tonne this
OL,9,Flast week.
OL,11,F"There are a lot of supplies that are
OL,12,Fstill needing to come into the country
OL,13,Fso there are going to be a fair number
OL,14,Fof farmers who are going to be short
OL,15,Fof fertiliser because it just isn't
OL,16,Fhere."
